{"tid":2098534,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"摩根大通將Tesla目標價上調至295美元","createTime":"2020-07-07T14:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T04:13:11.000Z","uid":54870,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f09c6b7e72e037a3858aa9e81e1d4cf6db1b2376","tid":2098534,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:17:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我冇打漏個1字</span></span><br />\n<br />\n摩根大通將Tesla目標價上調至295美元<br />\n並重申&ldquo;減持&rdquo;評級<br />\n<br />\n摩根大通 (JPMorgan) 分析師 Ryan Brinkman 週一將特斯拉股價目標上調 7.3%，至每股 295 美元，但仍比當前價格低 78%<br />\n<br />\nRyan Brinkman 提醒投資者，任何促成業績大幅改善的項目，可能包括一次性或某些上一次性項目，好比 FSD 遞延收入、監管信用額度等。<br />\n<br />\nRyan Brinkman 重申他至少在過去三年裡的「減持」股價評級，理由是特斯拉估值過高，加上投資者的高預期和高執行風險。<br />\n<br />\nRyan Brinkman 稱，我們的減持評級考慮明顯投資的積極因素，包括高度差異化的商業模式、吸引人的產品組合和領先技術，我們認為這些因素被過高的執行風險和估值所抵消，這似乎在很大程度反映定價上。"},{"pid":"4678b2c2dc710f19efe75c842c41140fa3ecec64","tid":2098534,"uid":20368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"離地到"},{"pid":"5dacbdc84d3856b0e5561239b8ff4bda868b3b66","tid":2098534,"uid":230196,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:24:07.000Z","msg":"個分析師瞓左幾年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb6ab88c7bd17ade06e6b45aab65d3ee4a8f9423","tid":2098534,"uid":76745,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dacbdc84d3856b0e5561239b8ff4bda868b3b66","tid":2098534,"uid":230196,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:24:07.000Z","msg":"個分析師瞓左幾年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:29:34.000Z","msg":"一時眼瞓打漏咗個1字喺前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4a25c2efed357d698a9a406f6a7e54a0405585f","tid":2098534,"uid":125976,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T14:32:21.000Z","msg":"我同 JP Morgan 嘅睇法一樣，數真係咁計，